 -- Function: np_to_matrix (A)
     Convert a 2D ndarray back to a Maxima matrix.

     The ndarray must be 2-dimensional.  For 1D ndarrays, use
     ‘np_to_list’ instead, or reshape to 2D first with ‘np_reshape’.
     Complex elements are returned in Maxima form (‘a + b*%i’).

