 -- Function: np_cov (A)
     Sample covariance matrix of a 2D ndarray.

     Treats each column as a variable and each row as an observation.
     Returns a p-by-p covariance matrix (where p is the number of
     columns) using the sample covariance formula (divides by n-1).  The
     result is symmetric.

