File: numerics.info,  Node: Design Notes,  Prev: Option Syntax,  Up: Package numerics

1.6 Design Notes
================

*Why not ‘np_reinforce’?*  REINFORCE has too many interacting callbacks
(policy mean, score function, noise injection, action clipping, initial
state sampler).  The symbolic ‘diff()’ step for the score function is
the key Maxima selling point -- hiding it in a library removes the
educational value.  Instead, use ‘np_rollout’ + ‘np_discount’ + a few
lines of user code.  ## Linear Algebra

